{"tid":1333511,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔我以你地為榮，多謝晒","createTime":"2019-07-19T17:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T07:51:14.000Z","uid":278176,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6e468eb40cc1cc5a89319dfa70f54c4874e897","tid":1333511,"uid":278176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:24:47.000Z","msg":"以一個癈中而言，以前只會間中睇下連登。一般遊行、佔中都會蒲頭。從未係連登開過po，但今日唔講過唔到自己。巴打、絲打你地真係好勁，個個都厲害勇敢。感激多謝你地付出守護香港，我冇乜野幫到手，只能略盡綿力課下金、遊下行。各位手足：我以你地為榮多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c567bbbb70682022b3d70b6f3828e368aea899e5","tid":1333511,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a187da09393984ed47048814165c457487d6e980","tid":1333511,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n「緊急號召」臨時立法會計劃書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333063\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333063</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【臨時議會】非法呀！出解放軍呀！冇人理你呀！未係時機呀！等外國支持呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332681\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成立臨時議會嘅時機，唔係等出嚟，係人民自己一手一腳造出嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1333314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1333314</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［721］認受性低都一定要宣布成立臨時立法會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1330843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1330843</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n7月21日   時代革命 成立臨時政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331101\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n重奪會將揭抗爭新一章，立刻準備manifesto!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1271540\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1271540</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[必須廣傳] 7.21 三點開記招！7.21 三點開記招！7.21 三點開記招！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329992\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[學術派] 組成國民議會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1289796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1289796</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n發夢寫咗一部香港憲法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327495\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n開始集體草擬一份屬於香港嘅民主憲法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324231</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>成立議會<br />\n已經係好多人嘅心聲<br />\n<br />\n721 新香港</strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"9b0ea7aad0c61d0558a0227bc50d5b1e6dd4b530","tid":1333511,"uid":231864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"唔使客氣 連登仔即係香港人<br />\n真香港人都會以真香港人為榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bcf02e27da790e741a299b36af6e9f2671eef1","tid":1333511,"uid":108751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:49:30.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n彩print好貴我明<br />\n整左簡陋黑白文宣幫大家慳d錢<br />\n係屋企印又得 出去印又平過彩色<br />\n快d盡情印盡情貼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQZyh72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQZyh72.jpg&h=42c0b983&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"694c113e6fbcd63ee84fb0cccb86943da879aa56","tid":1333511,"uid":278176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:48:54.000Z","msg":"我多謝大家，香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963371d9b7100832fb2458cd6b026fc116bee4e4","tid":1333511,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20